trans-unit.source: Hosts one or more <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference" /> elements that define a sequence of fixed documents.
<xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence> hosts an ordered sequence of one or more fixed documents that are organized as a single unit.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence> hospeda uma sequência ordenada de um ou mais documentos fixos são organizados como uma única unidade.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference> is the only allowable child element in a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference> é o elemento filho somente permitido em um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence>.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference> refers to a single <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>.
trans-unit.target: Cada <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference> se refere a um único <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>.

trans-unit.source: Document reference elements must be in sequential order, matching the order in which the fixed documents are processed.
trans-unit.target: Elementos de documento de referência devem ser em ordem sequencial, correspondência a ordem na qual os documentos fixos são processados.

trans-unit.source: A collection of the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference> elements contained in a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence> can be obtained using the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence.References%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção do <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference> elementos contidos em um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence> pode ser obtida usando o <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence.References%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The following example show how to obtain the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence> of an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> by use of the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument.GetFixedDocumentSequence%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostram como obter o <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence> de um <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> usando o <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument.GetFixedDocumentSequence%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" /> class.
Gets the paginator for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument" /> that provides page-oriented services such as getting a particular page and repaginating in response to changes.
An object of a class derived from <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentPaginator" /> that provides pagination services
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de uma classe derivada de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentPaginator" /> que fornece serviços de paginação

trans-unit.source: If you need a paginator with automatic repagination in responses to changes, such as adding content to the document, derive a class from <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DynamicDocumentPaginator> which itself inherits from <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentPaginator>.
trans-unit.target: Se você precisar de um paginator com repaginação automática em respostas a alterações, como adicionar conteúdo ao documento, derive uma classe de <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DynamicDocumentPaginator> que herda de <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentPaginator>.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator for accessing the document sequence's <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference" /> child elements.
An enumerator for accessing the document sequence's <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference" /> child elements.
trans-unit.target: Um enumerador para acessar a sequência de documento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentReference" /> elementos filho.

trans-unit.source: Creates an automation peer for the sequence.
A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer" /> that exposes the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" /> to Microsoft UI Automation.
Your derived version can return any <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer" />, it does not have to be a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Sua versão derivada pode retornar qualquer <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer" />, ele não precisa ser um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> that is associated with this document sequence.
The <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> for this sequence.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> para essa sequência.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> contains printing information such as whether to print on both sides of each sheet.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> contém informações de impressão, como se a impressão em ambos os lados de cada folha.

trans-unit.source: Setting this <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence.PrintTicket%2A> property does not validate or modify the specified <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> for a particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.
trans-unit.target: Essa configuração <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence.PrintTicket%2A> propriedade não validar ou modificar especificado <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> para um determinado <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.

trans-unit.source: If needed, use the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>-specific <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> that is valid for a given printer.
trans-unit.target: Se necessário, use o método <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A> para criar um <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> específico <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> que é válido para uma determinada impressora.
